textBox.richText: Closing day...Alli dressed up again as Jane. Did a front-side run with her and Max, then took off to the bowl. Got another 6" last night, but the temps stayed warm, so it was heavy powder. Had the S7's, and they did *great* with it. Did a bunch of Bowl laps (far side), and a bunch of laps through upper switchyard trees. Had to head over to c-lift for the closing madness...Alli and I met up with Max over there.
